data.description:
Rockwall ISD  --  Beautifully UPDATED Home with REAL Hardwood Floors installed in 2021.  4 Bedrooms 3 Full Baths with a Flex room Downstairs and a Game Room Upstairs.  Primary Suite is split from the 2 bedrooms downstairs.  Upstairs has a Game Room, Full Bath, and an Oversized Bedroom with a Walk in closet.  Kitchen Features updated Backsplash and Granite Countertops 2021, Stainless Steel appliances, Wood Cabinets, lots of Counter Space, and a Large Corner Pantry.  There is a Wood burning Fireplace in the Living Area.  Primary Bedroom has a Garden Tub and a Separate Shower.
Backyard has a board on board Fence updated in 2021,  Cedar Pergola, and lots of green space to enjoy.  The Roof was Replaced in 2023.   This Beautiful Home has Zero Carpet in the home and Real Hardwood Floors.  The Entrance is Arched with Stone and Has an Inviting Front Porch.
Travis Ranch has a Large Community Pool, Splash Park, Spacious Covered Pavilion, In-line Hockey Rink, Sports Fields, and Playground Area.
